f the store team is timely, accurate and uses all company systems; \n20. Ensure compliance with all aspects of the health & safety, and product safety policies; \n21. Ensure compliance with all aspects of the company’s audit and operating procedures; \n22. Be accountable for all financial anomalies recorded during your period of responsibility, reporting such anomalies to your line manager;\n23. Follow superior’s instruction for any new assignment/projects.', 
