p with new technological trends and ideas.\n5.' || chr(9) || 'Responsible for brand and products keywords SEM & SEO media channels, ensuring profitable ROI on investments.\n6.' || chr(9) || 'Responsible for E-commerce ROI-driven media channels (CPS, DSP, affiliation, EDM...).\nDigital Projects Implementation & Initiatives\n1.' || chr(9) || 'Lead/coordinate/monitor digital & E-commerce projects for China.\n2.' || chr(9) || 'Define digital strategy and priorities for China, across all digital building blocks.\n3.' || chr(9) || 'Provide strategic and technical support to other functions'' digital innovation and initiatives. \n4.' || chr(9) || 'Developing digital knowledge, expertise and evangelization of digital throughout the organization (online 2 offline activities, digital in point of sales, digital back-office productivity).\nAwareness & Image Building In Digital Platforms\n1.' || chr(9) || 'Owner of the digital real estate for C&A in China: website, mobile site, Tmall store, social media platform.\n2.' || chr(9) || 'Responsible to ensure and update creative design of these platforms always in line with brand''s creative guidelines, local marketing plan and digital trade activities.\n3.' || chr(9) || 'Responsible for digital content management and production to be displayed on all C&A digital assets in line with Marketing and Communication plans.\n4.' || chr(9) || 'Ensure CMS management to ensure timely update of local platform.\n5.' || chr(9) || 'Responsible for C&A presence on local Social networks (Wechat, Weibo TBC), driving social network animation plan for Wechat and support for Weibo, monitoring local implementation of the plan and performance and animating community management', 
